@node "Author      " "Author      "

Hi. It's been a long time since DiamondGUI wasn't updated. The fact that
I still getting some emails after almost a two years from last release,
asking when will be next version, showing me that interest in this
program still exist.
Well here it is. I put my efforts and made it, but this program is
now Giftware. It is fully functional, no limitations or nag requesters.
However, I spend a lot of time developing this program and if you
like it, and use it, please send me some money donation, or just some
gift (anything you want :) ). This will encourage me to continue
developing this program, and implement more nice features.

If you send me money donation, and program later become shareware, you
will get personal version, and your donation will be considered as
registration.


Address for gifts:

Nada Stepanovic
Tomice Popovica 52
11080 Zemun
Yugoslavia

And, if you have any comments or suggestions, my e-mail address is:
dexter@afrodita.rcub.bg.ac.yu.

Web page: http://www.geocities.com/diamond_gui

@endnode
